bash
Copy code
git push origin feature/add-dashboard-ui
Open a Pull Request (PR) on GitHub:

Target branch â†’ main

Add a meaningful title and short description

Request at least one reviewer

After approval, merge it safely through GitHub.

ðŸ§© Code Style Rules
Use Tailwind CSS + DaisyUI for all front-end styling.

Keep each component modular in /components/ui.

Always use .env files for secrets, never commit them.

Test locally before pushing (npm run dev).

All commits should follow the format:

makefile
Copy code
type(scope): message

Examples:
feat(dashboard): add vibrant animated background
fix(auth): resolve login redirect issue
âœ… Checklist Before Merging
 No console errors or warnings

 Proper component folder structure

 All routes work correctly

 Gradient background and UI animations function properly

 No .env or node_modules committed

